Using ${artifactId}

* Installation

  To use this library in your own Maven-based project, just add the following
to your <<<pom.xml>>>:

+--
    <dependency>
      <groupId>${groupId}</groupId>
      <artifactId>${artifactId}</artifactId>
      <version>${currentVersion}</version>
    </dependency>
+--

  You can also download the jar and its dependencies directly from 
Maven Central:

    * {{{http://repo2.maven.org/maven2/com/github/cwilper/fcrepo-store/${artifactId}/${currentVersion}/${artifactId}-${currentVersion}.jar}${artifactId}-${currentVersion}.jar}}

    * {{{./dependencies.html}All dependencies}}

